# This study is not evenly distributed, as balsam fir was overrepresented while black ash was very underrepresented
# It is important to recognize bias in ecological datasets, because underrepresentation may lead to inaccurate data. This may be because of mistaking outliers for the norm, or not getting a correctly sized range.
